text: Victor Negara (born 14 July 1991) is a Moldovan footballer who plays as a defender for Moldovan club Spartanii Selemet. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Moldovan footballers Category:Sportspeople from Chișinău Category:Association football defenders Category:Speranța Nisporeni players Category:FC Victoria Bardar players Category:FC Dinamo-Auto Tiraspol players Category:FC Zaria Bălți players Category:Moldovan National Division players
